items.name: open-alteryx-macro
items.description: Welcome to the 'Open-Alteryx-Macro' project. This project is aimed at providing an open-source solution for managing and updating Alteryx Macros.

items.name: cleanPyData
items.description: cleanPyData is a Python package for data cleaning and preprocessing. It handles missing values, normalizes data, extracts features, and detects outliers, making your data ready for analysis or machine learning.
